â€œSFV Dog is quickly becoming a staple strain for me. â€œI was surprised in a variety of ways by this potent strain. The taste was rather mellow and I found myself coughing considerably less than usual. The stoney head high is very relaxing and comforting, though I can't say it's anxiety-calming after a day's use. â€œBeautifully pungent skunky yet sweet aroma. â€œIf this is in your Dispensaries, try some. Personally one of my favorite go to meds that's been steady. Worth a Jimmy fart or 2 no doubtâ€
